{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC04_FRI_200.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x17,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x30,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Fritz, there's something I want you to teach me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Yes, I figured you would come sooner or later."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Huh...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x3e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "You came to ask about how to perform maintenance on Plachta, right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Oh, yes. That's right, but... How did you know?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Heh heh, of course I would. All I had to do was think about how important Plachta is to you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1b,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "...Ahaha, it's like you saw right through me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "I can pretty much read your thoughts at this point."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Anyway... How about I start teaching you about how to maintain her?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Yes, please."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "I call it maintenance, but it's actually not overly difficult to repair parts that start to have problems."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Most issues arise from small dislocations or abrasions of parts. They can be fixed without much work at all."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Hm, I didn't know that."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x17,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Usually, the hardest thing is actually finding which part is causing the issue."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x1a,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Dolls can't talk to you about it, after all. You need to investigate to find the problem... Normally, that is."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "...Oh, right. Plachta can..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Yes. Luckily for you, the doll you're maintaining isn't a normal doll. She can talk to you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x43,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "If you pay attention to her actions, and ask her how she feels, you should be able to locate the problem in no time."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "I see... Being able to ask about it is a lot easier than with a normal doll."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, that's the basic information you need to know. Now, you need to put it into practice."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x5,
            "name_id": 0x5,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "I'll show you how to service parts now, so be sure to watch carefully and learn."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x42,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Yes, I will, thank you!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x3,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x26,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "Fritz learned the skill \"<CLGR>Quick Action<CLNR>\"."
        }
    ]
}